name: Cluseller Style
description:
LORA trained on the art of Cluseller.

If you are familiar with vtubers, specifically the indie cooking vtuber named Onigiri, you may know this artist. Like JK's style, they often draw nicely emotive faces, though for cluseller you see this more with the teeth they draw. When training this, I tried to accurately capture the mouth detail, but I don't think I succeeded, unfortunately. Inpainting should probably help tho.

Better to keep this at a weight below 1.

100 images trained on NAI and tested across multiple models. Token requirement undetermined. Possibly NSFW capable.

Images in preview may be from past versions! Do not expect full replication!

Images you make with this model and what you do with them are your responsibility!
